Scope of redistribution — important context
================================================================================

This repository is NOT a stand-alone redistribution of NVIDIA CUDA Toolkit
components or any other third-party software. The binaries hosted here are
distribution infrastructure for the FieldCure software ecosystem — namely:

  * FieldCure.DocumentParsers.Audio (audio transcription library)
  * FieldCure.Mcp.Rag (retrieval-augmented generation MCP server)
  * FieldCure.AssistStudio (WinUI 3 AI chat application, where applicable)

These applications provide material additional functionality (audio
transcription, document parsing, semantic search, retrieval-augmented
generation, and conversational AI workflows) that goes substantially
beyond the redistributed components themselves. The redistributable
components are accessed only by these applications and their authorized
consumers.


