4. Vulkan
================================================================================

The Vulkan-flavored Whisper binary (ggml-vulkan-whisper.dll) is built
against the Vulkan API. This repository does NOT redistribute the Vulkan
loader itself (vulkan-1.dll); the Vulkan loader is supplied by the user's
GPU driver installation and is loaded dynamically at runtime.

For reference, the upstream Vulkan Loader is published by The Khronos
Group at https://github.com/KhronosGroup/Vulkan-Loader under the
Apache License 2.0, but no Vulkan Loader binaries are present in this
repository's releases.


